      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a superlative E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 3.2L inline-six remains in peak mechanical health, with the double VANOS system meticulously serviced and individual throttle bodies synchronized for razor-sharp response. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, feeding a factory limited-slip differential. This chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Every suspension bushing and damper is within factory tolerances, maintaining the original kinematics. The exterior retains its showroom depth with zero oxidation or swirling, while the cabin is free of typical Nappa leather bolster wear or pixel degradation in the instrumentation. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example for the discerning enthusiast.",
